development, and one of the most sought-after prizes in academia: the Nobel Prize.

00:00:33.690 --> 00:00:38.550
In October this year, three economists won the top prize in economics for

00:00:38.559 --> 00:00:44.330
groundbreaking work into the root cause of a country’s prosperity, or lack of it.

00:00:44.890 --> 00:00:50.380
Their theories are fascinating, so in the next 20 minutes or so we’ll talk about

